data.description: Great area for a custom home. Over one acre in a great location. Just a short walk to Southport High School and grade schools. Located close to shopping and dining. The subject property is two parcels just south of Buck Creek, on the NE corner of Southport Road and Shelby Street. Buyer will need to verify elevations, survey, and the viability of blueprints. Possibility of more than one building lots.
